p: Since the 30 and 60 min enzyme treatments of Catfish frames were not significantly different, for the Catfish head treatment, shorter time periods were examined. Moisture content of both the 5‐ and 30‐min enzyme treatments of the Catfish head bone were significantly larger than the 0‐min enzyme treatment (Table 2); however, only the 30‐min treatment was larger than the untreated head bone.
